<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Avoid the intersection of overlapping labels.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Automatically adjust the position of labels.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Customize the appearance of labels.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features
</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Palette"</Bold> helps to apply palette for ChartArea.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Show Smart Labels</Bold> check box enables the smart label support.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Adornment Intersection</Bold> combo box changes the type of intersection available for the smart labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Symbol</Bold> combo box changes the symbol type for the smart labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Symbol Interior</Bold> combo box to change the color of the smart labels.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Chart Types</Bold> combo box changes the type of chart in which the data series is plotted.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>IsIndexed</Bold> check box enables the indexed support for the series.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>Y Axis IsInversed</Bold> check box enables inversed support for the y-axis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>X Axis IsInversed</Bold> check box enables inversed support for the x-axis.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>

